beer.beer_description:
Hops: Riwaka/Waimea/NZ Cascade

Believe us when we say we intended this beer to be clear…and it turned out as planned! We have to write the labels before we see the final result so when you read the can you can tell we were a bit unsure.

Nay bother, the whole way through ferment and dry-hopping this Imperial IPA was tasting on point and now we have the added bonus of it looking the way we had intended. Plus, we found our new favourite way to use Riwaka.
